Python script that checks the device file for botton code.
For each code it will do some actions in the system.

Main:
cubie_irda.py -- main script

Optional:
irda_scan_botton.py -- script for grubbing botton code to a file for future use.
It can be usefull for detecting the botton code for using in main script.

USAGE:

Just start the script in cmd or put it to autostart.
Infinity loop will check the device file all the time.
